<paragraph id="F1053680FFCCF540FF715C59673AFACD" blockId="19.[151,1437,1005,1321]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">
Type data: 
<bibRefCitation id="952B4B71FFCCF540FEFF5C586582FBE5" author="Smith, F." box="[281,432,1041,1068]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" pagination="199 - 465" refId="ref19938" refString="Smith, F. (1854) Catalogue of Hymenopterous Insects in the Collection of the British Museum. Part 2. British Museum, London, 267 pp. [pp. 199 - 465]" type="book chapter" year="1854">Smith (1854)</bibRefCitation>
described this species based on an undetermined number of females. 
<bibRefCitation id="952B4B71FFCCF540FB3A5C59651FFB98" author="Moure, J. S. &amp; Seabra, C. A. C." pageId="19" pageNumber="170" pagination="1 - 13" refId="ref19492" refString="Moure, J. S. &amp; Seabra, C. A. C. (1962) Tres especies novas de Centris (Ptilotopus) Klug, 1810 (Hymenoptera-Apoidea). Bole- tim Universidade Federal do Parana, Zoologia, 1 (14), 1 - 13." type="journal article" year="1962">Moure &amp; Seabra (1962)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned that the type of this species was housed at 
<collectionCode id="97ABAE45FFCCF540FC475C7D603CFB98" box="[929,1038,1079,1105]" country="United Kingdom" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34665" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34665" name="Natural History Museum, London" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" type="Museum">NHMUK</collectionCode>
, providing information on the data label of provenance. Moure &amp; Seabra’s interpretation can be treated as a valid 
<typeStatus id="2E018822FFCCF540FBAB5C106086FBBD" box="[1101,1204,1114,1140]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">lectotype</typeStatus>
designation, according to 
<collectionCode id="97ABAE45FFCCF540FECB5C34655CFB51" box="[301,366,1150,1176]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">ICZN</collectionCode>
(1999) Article number 74.6. The specimen has the following data label: 
<taxonomicName id="36BA4D03FFCCF540FB565C3560CCFB51" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1854" box="[1200,1278,1151,1176]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sponsa">
<emphasis id="C3CEEA92FFCCF540FB565C3560CCFB51" box="[1200,1278,1151,1176]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">sponsa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Sm Columb. [handwritten]\ Colum [handwritten]\ [black-rimmed label] 
<typeStatus id="2E018822FFCCF540FC905CE867ECFB75" box="[886,990,1186,1212]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Holotype</typeStatus>
[printed] 
<taxonomicName id="36BA4D03FFCCF540FBAB5CE9612DFB75" authority="Sm" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1854" box="[1101,1311,1186,1213]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sponsa">
<emphasis id="C3CEEA92FFCCF540FBAB5CE960C6FB75" box="[1101,1268,1187,1213]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Centris sponsa</emphasis>
Sm
</taxonomicName>
[handwritten] J. S. Moure [printed] 1957 [handwritten]\ Named as 
<taxonomicName id="36BA4D03FFCCF540FCBA5C8D60B8FB29" authority="Smith 1854" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1854" box="[860,1162,1221,1249]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sponsa">
<emphasis id="C3CEEA92FFCCF540FCBA5C8D6031FB29" box="[860,1027,1223,1249]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Centris sponsa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="952B4B71FFCCF540FBEF5C8C60B8FB29" author="Smith, F." box="[1033,1162,1221,1248]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" pagination="199 - 465" refId="ref19938" refString="Smith, F. (1854) Catalogue of Hymenopterous Insects in the Collection of the British Museum. Part 2. British Museum, London, 267 pp. [pp. 199 - 465]" type="book chapter" year="1854">
Smith 
<quantity id="36429B65FFCCF540FBB45C8F60B8FB29" box="[1106,1162,1221,1248]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.70916" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" unit="in" value="1854.0">1854</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
in W.W. Saunders colln. OX. 
<collectionCode id="97ABAE45FFCCF540FEF65CA06576FACD" box="[272,324,1258,1284]" country="0" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/xxq3-2kv6" name="University of Northern Iowa" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">UNI</collectionCode>
.MUS.NAT. 
<collectionCode id="97ABAE45FFCCF540FE2F5CA06638FACD" box="[457,522,1258,1284]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">HIST</collectionCode>
. (
<collectionCode id="97ABAE45FFCCF540FDFA5CA066BFFACD" box="[540,653,1258,1284]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">OUMNH</collectionCode>
). [printed].
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F1053680FFCCF540FF715D45659DFAE1" blockId="19.[151,1437,1005,1321]" box="[151,431,1294,1321]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">
<materialsCitation id="41D23CDDFFCCF540FF715D456599FAE1" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="2561482884" box="[151,427,1294,1321]" country="Colombia" location="Colombia" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" specimenCount="1" typeStatus="holotype">
<typeStatus id="2E018822FFCCF540FF715D4564FDFAE0" box="[151,207,1295,1321]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Type</typeStatus>
locality: 
<collectingCountry id="89AD7610FFCCF540FEDF5D446599FAE1" box="[313,427,1294,1320]" name="Colombia" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Colombia</collectingCountry>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F1053680FFCCF540FF715D1C670BF9C9" blockId="19.[151,1437,1366,1537]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">
Comments: According to the original description and the information on the label, the 
<typeStatus id="2E018822FFCCF540FB865D1C60F5FAB9" box="[1120,1223,1366,1392]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">lectotype</typeStatus>
specimen was collected in 
<collectingCountry id="89AD7610FFCCF540FEE65D306543FA5D" box="[256,369,1402,1428]" name="Colombia" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Colombia</collectingCountry>
, but this species has never been recorded in northern South America (
<bibRefCitation id="952B4B71FFCCF540FB6C5D3061A3FA5D" author="Velez, D. &amp; Vivallo, F." box="[1162,1425,1402,1428]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" pagination="46 - 63" refId="ref20881" refString="Velez, D. &amp; Vivallo, F. (2018) Sinopsis de las especies del subgenero Centris (Ptilotopus) (Hymenoptera: Apidae) en Colombia. Biota Colombiana, 19 (2), 46 - 63. https: // doi. org / 10.21068 / c 2018. v 19 n 02 a 05" type="journal article" year="2018">Vélez &amp; Vivallo, 2018</bibRefCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName id="36BA4D03FFCCF540FF715DD56572FA71" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1854" box="[151,320,1439,1465]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sponsa">
<emphasis id="C3CEEA92FFCCF540FF715DD56572FA71" box="[151,320,1439,1465]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Centris sponsa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in northeastern and southeastern 
<collectingCountry id="89AD7610FFCCF540FCEB5DD46763FA71" box="[781,849,1438,1464]" name="Brazil" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="952B4B71FFCCF540FC875DD46077FA71" author="Silveira, F. A. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Almeida, E. A. B." box="[865,1093,1438,1465]" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" refId="ref19793" refString="Silveira, F. A., Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Almeida, E. A. B. (2002) Abelhas brasileiras Sistematica e Identificacao. Fundacao Araucaria, Belo Horizonte, 254 pp." type="book" year="2002">
Silveira 
<emphasis id="C3CEEA92FFCCF540FC275DD567C1FA71" box="[961,1011,1438,1464]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">et al</emphasis>
., 2002
</bibRefCitation>
), so is very likely that the 
<typeStatus id="2E018822FFCCF540FA945DD464EFFA14" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">lectotype</typeStatus>
was mislabeled (as well as in 
<taxonomicName id="36BA4D03FFCCF540FDD85D8966D4FA15" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1854" box="[574,742,1474,1501]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="170" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maculifrons">
<emphasis id="C3CEEA92FFCCF540FDD85D896663FA14" box="[574,593,1475,1501]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">C</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="C3CEEA92FFCCF540FD875D8866D4FA15" box="[609,742,1474,1500]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">maculifrons</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, see above) thus incorrectly recorded in 
<collectingCountry id="89AD7610FFCCF540FB5C5D88611EFA15" box="[1210,1324,1474,1500]" name="Colombia" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Colombia</collectingCountry>
. The type locality cannot be further narrowed down than to 
<collectingCountry id="89AD7610FFCCF540FD245DAC6706F9C9" box="[706,820,1510,1536]" name="Colombia" pageId="19" pageNumber="170">Colombia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
